⸻

Definition

Stewards in u-Kama constitute the operational layer of custodianship.

They are responsible for maintaining the ecological conditions under which Protection and Regeneration can occur.

Stewards do not own the land and do not control ecological truth.
They maintain the conditions under which ecological truth may emerge and be witnessed.

⸻

